== 製作 ==
[[File:Oliver_Stone_01.jpg|thumb]]（圖片為1987年）為《疤面煞星》寫劇本的同時還為自己對[[可卡因|可卡因]]成癮而掙扎。]]
[[阿爾·柏仙奴|阿爾·柏仙奴]]在洛杉磯的{{link-en|蒂芙尼劇院|Tiffany Theater}}觀看過1932年的英文同名電影《[[傷面人|傷面人]]》後，便開始開發《疤面煞星》。後來他打電話給他的經紀人、監製{{link-en|馬丁·布萊格曼|Martin Bregman}}，並告訴布萊格曼重拍這部電影的可能性。<ref name="Movieline">{{Cite web |url = http://movieline.com/2011/08/24/al-pacino-did-not-want-michelle-pfeiffer-for-scarface-and-8-other-revelations-about-the-gangster-cla/ |title = Al Pacino Did Not Want Michelle Pfeiffer For Scarface and 8 Other Revelations About the Gangster Classic |date = 2011-08-24 |publisher = Movieline |language = en |accessdate = 2018-04-19 |archive-date = 2013-12-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131208051505/http://movieline.com/2011/08/24/al-pacino-did-not-want-michelle-pfeiffer-for-scarface-and-8-other-revelations-about-the-gangster-cla/ |dead-url = yes }}</ref>柏仙奴原本想保留電影中那段歷史時期的部分，但卻意識到由於它的誇張性質，所以很難去實現。[[薛尼·盧密|薛尼·盧密]]成為導演，開發了有關在[[馬列爾事件|馬列爾事件]]期間古巴人東尼·莫塔納抵達美國的概念。<ref name="Movieline" />

布萊格曼和盧密的創作差異導致盧密退出該項目。盧密希望做出一個更政治化的故事，集中在指責現任總統的政府令可卡因大量湧入美國，而布萊格曼則不同意盧密的觀點。布萊格曼用[[白賴仁·狄龐馬|白賴仁·狄龐馬]]取代盧密，並聘請編劇[[奧利華·史東|奧利華·史東]]，後來表示只用了四通電話來確保他們的參與。史東看過原本的1932年《傷面人》，而且不喜歡這部電影，所以他最初拒絕了該提議<ref name="David Konow">{{Cite web |url = https://creativescreenwriting.com/writing-in-a-very-dark-room-oliver-stone-revisits-scarface/ |title = Writing in a Very Dark Room – Oliver Stone revisits Scarface |author = David Konow |date = 2015-01-20 |publisher = creativescreenwriting.com |language = en |accessdate = 2018-04-19 |archive-date = 2017-12-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171216034939/https://creativescreenwriting.com/writing-in-a-very-dark-room-oliver-stone-revisits-scarface/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。直到他與盧密交談後，他才接受這一提議，因為他們同意將該電影從以前的時代轉變成一部當代電影<ref name="David Konow" />，說：「薛尼有一個好主意，可以把1930年代美國禁酒令的黑幫電影製作成一部現代移民黑幫電影，涉及同樣問題，而我們用禁毒代替禁酒。禁毒與禁酒創造了同樣的犯罪類型，就像黑手黨。」<ref name="David Konow" />史東在應付自己的可卡因成癮的同時研究了劇本<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.shortlist.com/entertainment/films/15-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-scarface/86316#item-12 |title = 15 Things You (Probably) Didn’t Know About Scarface |publisher = ShortList |language = en |accessdate = 2018-04-19 |archive-date = 2018-04-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180419183713/https://www.shortlist.com/entertainment/films/15-things-you-probably-didnt-know-about-scarface/86316#item-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他和布萊格曼做了他們自己的研究，前往佛羅里達州的邁阿密，在那裡他們獲得機會看到美國檢察官辦公室和有組織犯罪局的記錄。史東搬到巴黎寫劇本，認為他在美國時無法切斷他的成癮，在2003年的一次採訪中說他當時完全脫離毒品，「因為我不認為可卡因有助於寫作，這是對腦細胞具有非常破壞性的。」

==續集==
2001年，傳出片商將計劃推出《疤面煞星》的續集，名為《東尼之子》（''Son of Tony''），並由嘻哈歌手{{link-en|古巴·林克|Cuban Link}}主演<ref name="Ozone">{{cite web |url=http://www.ozonemag.com/feb2002/cubanlink.html |title=Son of Tony |accessdate=2007-01-02|work=Ozone Magazine| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927133005/http://www.ozonemag.com/feb2002/cubanlink.html | archivedate = 2011-09-27| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。但計劃引起了網上正反兩極的反應，幾年後，古巴·林克表示，他可能不再參與該計劃，主要因為版權和創意控制等問題<ref name="LatinRapper">{{cite web |url=http://www.latinrapper.com/featurednews41.html|title=Cuban Link Starts His Chain Reaction|accessdate=2007-01-02|work=Latin Rapper| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140402165713/http://latinrapper.com/featurednews41.html | archivedate = 2014-04-02| deadurl=no}}</ref>。之後，續集的計劃並未有更進一步的消息，因此被認為已作廢。

==重拍版==
2011年，環球影業宣布，他們正在發展一部新版的《疤面煞星》電影。官方表示，這部片既不是續集也不是重拍，而是一部全新的電影，但它將會採用1932年電影《[[疤面|疤面]]》的元素。而馬丁·布萊格曼則也將監製1983年版本電影的重拍<ref>{{cite news|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|location=United States|publisher={{link-en|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}}|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/universal-pictures-readying-a-new-scarface/|title=Universal Preps New ‘Scarface’ Movie|date=2011-09-21|archivedate=2011-09-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105230303/http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/universal-pictures-readying-a-new-scarface/|accessdate=2013-11-05 }}</ref>，劇本由[[大衛·艾亞|大衛·艾亞]]負責<ref>{{cite news|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|location=United States|publisher={{link-en|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}}|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/11/david-ayer-to-script-updated-scarface/|title= David Ayer To Script Updated ‘Scarface’date=|date=2011-11-29|archivedate=2011-11-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407233049/http://www.deadline.com/2011/11/david-ayer-to-script-updated-scarface/|accessdate=2014-04-07}}</ref>，而[[大衛·葉慈|大衛·葉慈]]正在會談擔任導演<ref>{{cite news|first=Nikki|last=Finke|url=http://deadline.com/2013/07/david-yates-in-final-talks-for-scarface-as-universal-very-high-on-reboot-script/|title=David Yates In Final Talks For ‘Scarface’ Helm Now Universal “Very High” On Script|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|location=United States|publisher={{link-en|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407233042/http://deadline.com/2013/07/david-yates-in-final-talks-for-scarface-as-universal-very-high-on-reboot-script/|date=2013-07-31|archivedate=2013-07-31|accessdate=2014-04-07}}</ref>。

2014年3月24日，[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]報導，[[帕布羅·拉瑞恩|帕布羅·拉瑞恩]]在會談執導電影，而劇本是由{{link-en|保羅·艾登納西歐|Paul Attanasio}}負責。這部電影將會是一個原創的故事，被設定於現代的[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，敘述墨西哥移民為了實現自己的美國夢而在黑社會中崛起<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/scarface-remake-director-pablo-larrain-says-yes-universal/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: Spider-Man 4 Circling John Malkovich, Anne Hathaway|work=[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]|publisher=The Wrap News Inc.|location=[[聖塔莫尼卡|Santa Monica, California]]|date=2014-03-24|accessdate=2014-03-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421185247/http://www.thewrap.com/scarface-remake-director-pablo-larrain-says-yes-universal/|archivedate=2014-04-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>。強納森·赫曼於2015年3月被聘來為劇本的初稿進行重寫<ref>{{cite news|last1=Siegel|first1=Tatian|title='Scarface' Remake Moving Forward With 'Straight Outta Compton' Writer (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarface-remake-moving-forward-straight-782472|accessdate=2015-03-22|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|location=United States|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320150856/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarface-remake-moving-forward-straight-782472|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年8月10日，[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]報導，[[安東尼·法奎|安東尼·法奎]]正在會談執導新版《疤面煞星》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/scarface-antoine-fuqua-remake-universal-al-pacino-1201801594/|title=Antoine Fuqua Circling New ‘Scarface’ At Universal|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|location=United States|publisher={{link-en|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}}|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|date=2016-08-10|accessdate=2017-02-11|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811110216/http://deadline.com/2016/08/scarface-antoine-fuqua-remake-universal-al-pacino-1201801594/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月28日，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》報導，[[泰倫斯·溫特|泰倫斯·溫特]]將為電影撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/terence-winter-scarface-reimagining-antoine-fuqua-1201872923/|title=‘Wolf of Wall Street’ Scribe to Write Antoine Fuqua’s ‘Scarface’ Reimagining (EXCLUSIVE)|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|location=United States|publisher={{link-en|潘斯奇媒體公司|Penske Media Corporation|Penske Media Corporation}}|last=Fleming, Jr|first=Mike|date=2016-08-10|accessdate=2017-02-11|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216033055/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/terence-winter-scarface-reimagining-antoine-fuqua-1201872923/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月，法奎退出了該計劃，而電影男主角則由[[狄亞哥·盧納|狄亞哥·盧納]]飾演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieweb.com/scarface-remake-cast-diego-luna-director-antoine-fuqua/|title=Diego Luna Is the New Scarface, Director Antoine Fuqua Exits|work=Movie Web|location=United States|publisher=Watchr Media|last=Scott|first=Ryan|date=2017-01-31|accessdate=2017-02-11|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081921/http://movieweb.com/scarface-remake-cast-diego-luna-director-antoine-fuqua/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月10日，宣布該電影將於2018年8月10日在美國上映，而劇本則由[[柯恩兄弟|柯恩兄弟]]負責<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/813251-scarface-remake-gets-coen-brothers-script-release-date|title=Scarface Remake Gets Coen Brothers Script, Release Date|date=2017-02-10|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210220401/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/813251-scarface-remake-gets-coen-brothers-script-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年5月，[[盧卡·格達戈尼諾|盧卡·格達戈尼諾]]接手擔任導演<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/luca-guadagnino-scarface-reboot-director-universal-1203452103/|title=Luca Guadagnino to Direct ‘Scarface’ Reboot|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=Variety|date=2020-05-14|accessdate=2020-05-17|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516110855/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/luca-guadagnino-scarface-reboot-director-universal-1203452103/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

